	gdk/src/devicemanager.hg: Deprecate list_devices() and get_client_pointer().
	gdk/src/display.[hg|ccg]: Deprecate get_device_manager(). Add list_seats(),
	get_default_seat(), signal_seat_added() and signal_seat_removed().
