	* atk/atkmm/Makefile.am (local_cppflags): Append -DATKMM_BUILD=1.
	* gdk/gdkmm/Makefile.am (local_cppflags): Append -DGDKMM_BUILD=1.
	* gtk/gtkmm/Makefile.am (local_cppflags): Append -DGTKMM_BUILD=1.

