2007-05-23  Jonathon Jongsma  <jjongsma@gnome.org>

	renamed the gmmproc appendix to "Wrapping C Libraries with gmmproc" so

2007-05-23  Jonathon Jongsma  <jjongsma@gnome.org>

	* docs/tutorial/gtkmm-tut.xml: renamed the gmmproc appendix to "Wrapping C
