2005-07-10  Murray Cumming  <murrayc@murrayc.com>

	Regenerated with h2defs.py

2005-07-10  Murray Cumming  <murrayc@murrayc.com>

	* gdk/src/gdk_methods.defs: Regenerated with h2defs.py
	* gdk/src/cursor.ccg:
	* gdk/src/cursor.hg: Added get_image() and
	a Cursor(name) constructor.
